column5: A little video of the musky fishing in the Ottawa River with the Silveradosheriff last oct. Enjoy!
Love the music Nice one there for SS.
Cool muskie fishing video !!!.  ..nice catch as well...cheers
Cool video, thanks for sharing that.  Joey

Very nice! Looks like you caught a couple nice ones. I'm not asking for your honey hole, but what area were you in? Close to Arnprior? My dad wants me to go muskie fishing in the Ottawa with him. Thanks for posting.
Thanks, we fished the Hawksbury  east of Ottawa, Very nice area.Hoping to go again next year.
